Guinea’s New Mining Code Ready to Be Submitted, President Alpha Conde Says

-- B y   O u g n a   C a m a r a
-- 
2011-07-26T22:12:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/guinea-s-new-mining-code-ready-to-be-submitted-president-alpha-conde-says.html
Guinea President  Alpha Conde  said a
new mining code will be submitted for adoption to the National
Council of Transition, the west African nation’s equivalent of
parliament.  “The new code is ready,” Conde said in speech broadcast
by the state-owned Radio Television Guineenne. He did not say
when the code will be debated.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  